LD toolbox manual. H.W. IMB-Graz. University of Graz. 

Interactive editor shortcuts:

LD finder:
Left-mouse click=select cross.
Right-mouse click=delete cross.  
Add cross=double left mouse click.
y=enlarge position helper (when cross selected).
c=shrink position helper (when cross selected).

LD descriptor:
left-mouse click=select circle.
+key=enlarge selected circle.
-key=shrink selected circle.
Hold left-mouse button+drag=move circle. 
right-mouse click=delete selected circle.
b=contrast-based batch removal of selected structure / u=undo.
p=undo automatic object centre refinement.
